name: Dear Silent Sea
description:
When everything that breathes are now, perish
When mankind leaves their mortal coil and thus, 
finish

And the stars and spaces collide, 
ashes to ashes and dust to dust

I lay dormant for my final judgement 

from desert of eternity to silent red sea


--painting inspired by my favorite artist, yeule, and one of my favorite movie, 
the end of evangelion
